1.0.0.name: wordpress/wpml-page-order
1.0.0.description:
"WPML page order" plugin is not supported, because "WPML" plugin is not free anymore.

"WPML page order" plugin helps you to set up the order of pages with drag-and-drop interface. Order of translated pages updates automatically.
